	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissime.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Veniens ad vos frater iste vester et meus in Christo<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Johannes Haller</persName>.</note> necesse non erat, ut aliquid scriberem; poterat enim ipsemet oretenus tue humanitati animum meum erga te exprimere, sed ex abundantia cordis coactus sum tibi tum occupatissimo tum doctissimo meis illiteratis literis obstrepere notumque facere, quatenus te plurimum in Christo diligo, quod credere mihi debes vel experientiam facere.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rogoque te, ut, si me diligis, quam citius remittas ad nos fratrem istum; est enim modestia, virtus, doctrina et pietas sua talis, ut et inimici (si aliqui sunt) cogantur eum diligere.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Erimus enim ut fratres in Christo coniunctissimi, dignaberisque nomine meo salutare fratres omnes in Christo, praecipue <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicanum</persName>, mei memor in tuis orationibus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augusta</placeName>, 4. ianuarii 1546.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[ibi] d[editus]</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p2336" cert="high">Bernardinus Ochinus</persName> Senensis</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo domino <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Henrico Bullingero</persName>, theologo osservandissimo.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Johannes Haller</persName> nahm diesen Brief bei seiner Rückreise nach <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Zürich</placeName> mit.</note>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
